<h2 id="1-pipes">1. Pipes</h2>

<p>Pipes are animated screen savers</p>

<p>To install:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">git clone https://github.com/pipeseroni/pipes.sh.git
<span class="nb">cd </span>pipes.sh
<span class="nb">sudo </span>make <span class="nb">install</span></code></pre></figure>

<!-- QUADRADO -->
