<p><ins class="adsbygoogle" style="display:inline-block;width:336px;height:280px" data-ad-client="ca-pub-2838251107855362" data-ad-slot="5351066970"></ins>
<script>
(adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});
</script></p>

<p>Then run <code class="highlighter-rouge">pipes.sh</code> on the terminal, to exit press the <code class="highlighter-rouge">q</code> key. For more information and parameters see the manual section 6 page: <code class="highlighter-rouge">man 6 pipes.sh</code>.</p>

<p><img src="/assets/img/wm/pipes.sh.png" alt="pipes" /></p>

